flowchart TD
    A([Visitor]) --> B{Landing}
    B -->|Browse courses| C[Catalogue]
    B -->|Read about| D[About / Tutors]
    B -->|Sign in| E[Login]
    B -->|Sign up| F[Register]

    F -->|Email confirm| G[Active account]
    E --> G
    G --> H[Dashboard]

    %% Course-level (payment)
    C -->|Click course| I[Course detail]
    I -->|Enroll| I1[Stripe Checkout]
    I1 -->|Failed| I2[Enrollment pending]
    I2 -->|Retry| I1
    I1 -->|Succeeded| I3[enrollment = active]
    I3 --> H2[Course dashboard]

    %% Module-level (live session)
    H2 -->|Pick module| J[Module list]
    J -->|Choose slot| K[Calendly embed per module]
    K -->|Webhook| L[module_bookings scheduled]
    L -->|n8n + Zoom| M[Zoom meeting created]
    M -->|Confirmation email| N[Student notified]
    N --> O[Upcoming modules]

    O -->|T-24h| P[Reminder email]
    P -->|T-1h| Q[Reminder email]
    Q -->|At start| R[Join Zoom]
    R -->|meeting.ended| S[Module completed]
    S --> T{All modules<br/>completed?}
    T -->|No| J
    T -->|Yes| U[Enrollment completed]
    U --> V[Course resources unlocked]

    %% Side actions
    O -->|Cancel a module| W[Zoom voided, no refund]
    O -->|Reschedule a module| X[New slot, new Zoom]
    O -->|Refund a course| Y[Stripe refund at course level<br/>enrollment = refunded]

    %% Re-enrollment
    U -->|Re-enroll| I1
    Y -->|Re-enroll| I1
